<quantity metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.34" pageId="4" pageNumber="87" unit="m" value="3340.0">3340 m</quantity>
) in Guercif Province, 
<collectingCountry box="[426,527,339,365]" name="Morocco" pageId="4" pageNumber="87">Morocco</collectingCountry>
(
<figureCitation box="[547,619,338,365]" captionStart="FIGURE 5" captionStartId="4.[136,229,2029,2051]" captionTargetBox="[182,1382,1073,1987]" captionTargetId="figure-392@4.[172,1415,1073,2005]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURE 5. Geographic distribution of Centaurea species from sect. Melanoloma in Morocco: ●C. achilleifolia; ▲C. peltieri; C. takredensis; ■C. atlantis; C. gattefossei; C. oriolii-bolosii." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6404632" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6404632/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="87">Fig. 5</figureCitation>
